      <p class="guide-sub">Montgomery County has some of the highest DSCR ratios in Ohio. Low acquisition costs and consistent Wright-Patterson AFB rental demand make Dayton a strong cash-flow market.</p>
      <div class="guide-meta">
        <span class="guide-meta-item">Viador Partners, NMLS #2822744</span>
