        <button class="faq-q" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">Does Wright-Patterson AFB create reliable rental demand?</button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. Wright-Patterson is the Air Force's largest single installation, with a large permanent party population that generates consistent demand for off-base housing. Military tenants are generally stable, with regular income and accountability structures that many landlords prefer.</p></div>
